Description:
Since the establishment of the AWD Interior company in 2002, we have been creating timeless collections of bathroom accessories and interior design elements. Our assortment includes over 600 products from over a dozen categories signed with our own company brand. We place the main emphasis on the creation process:

- we provide high quality, taking into account the careful selection of materials and precision of workmanship, aesthetic value and durability;
- we design products with an attractive and original design, at the same time their universal nature fits in with the current interior design trends;
- we often expand our offer with new designs that meet the various requirements and tastes of customers;
- we make sure that our products are ergonomic and have additional functionalities that make them user-friendly and better suited to the needs of users.
As an international company, we are active in dozens of European countries. The experience gained over the years allows us to constantly modernize our offer to the current market trends and provide our business partners with a wide range of benefits. It includes, among other things, access to constantly updated inventory and the care of our sales representatives present in the country and abroad. We provide the possibility of using a modern, online B2B platform that facilitates the efficient execution of orders. Our partners are both large retail chains as well as medium and small enterprises. In our activities, we strive to strengthen business relations with contractors, which are the basis for long-term and fruitful cooperation.

The purpose of CEFACD is to study – primarily from a scientific, technical, pedagogical, economic and institutional point of view – topics of common interest to the domestic individual heating appliances, stoves, fireplaces, cooking appliances and related equipment industries and to represent and promote efficient and environmentally friendly individual heating appliances and cooking appliances and to safeguard the supranational interests of members as appropriate, in particular by:
- exchanging information and experiences on issues that are important to the industry;
- conducting joint technical and economic activities in order to ensure a level playing field for competition;
- cooperating with similar national, European, international and worldwide associations
- representing and promoting its members’ common economic, technical and political interests before the European Commission, the European Council, the European Parliament and other European and international bodies.

Departamentul intern și experimentat de Cercetare, dezvoltare și inginerie, unic în Europa, reprezintă principalul atu al companiei noastre.

Această concentrare pe dezvoltarea de noi produse a avut ca rezultat numeroase brevete, mărci înregistrate și modele pregătite pentru piață, printre care friteuza Frytastic (2013), Combi Waffle (2009), Fondue (2007), Turbo SF (2001), Sistemul Covering (2000), Sistemul Click (1997).

Atunci când proiectăm și dezvoltăm produsele FRITEL, misiunea și filozofia noastră implică nu doar oferirea unor performanțe remarcabile, ci și crearea unei ușurințe excelente în utilizare, asigurând în același timp o întreținere ușoară și oferind un design modern.

De la lansarea FRITEL în 1991, am dezvoltat o gamă largă de produse electrocasnice de succes:

- Seria Prăjire: Friteuza noastră Frytastic a fost selectată drept cea mai bună friteuză de către o revistă independentă de specialitate, în decembrie 2014;

- Seria Coacere: Aparate de făcut napolitane, aparate de făcut sandvișuri, grătare și grătare de masă;

- Seria Gătit distractiv: Fondue, Raclette și grătare de piatră, Teppanyaki, Raclette cu brânză;

- Serii Gătit: Blender, Tocător, Presă de citrice, Cuțit electric.

FRITEL, Creat cu gust!
